    "title": "WorldAgroCommodities (WAC) Processing Pipeline",
    "description": "This workflow is an end-to-end openEO pipeline for agricultural feature extraction and model inference using Sentinel-1 and Sentinel-2 data, a suite of preprocessing steps, vegetation indices, and a sliding-window ONNX model. The ML models were trained to classify agriculture activity for specific commodities in Africa, South-America or South-East Asia in the context of ESA's World AgroCommodities project",
